text: Arthur Fagan (10 December 1890 - 8 July 1977) was a British fencer. He competed in the individual foil event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1890 births Category:1977 deaths Category:British male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Great Britain Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Chertsey
